Kosciusko Street (right)? north side, east from Marcy Avenue.

text:
Kosciuszco Street, at Marcy Avenue. View 1 is east from Marcy Ave., showing the north side of the street. View 2 is west from Marcy Ave. and shows also the north side of the street.

August 30, 1941
Views 1,2
